00:31:06.300 --> 00:31:09.890
So you can just
replace this phi x

00:31:09.890 --> 00:31:15.035
by the boundary
value of capital phi.

00:31:17.660 --> 00:31:19.970
So this is for the scalar case.

00:31:19.970 --> 00:31:27.340
And you could write it
