00:31:47.819 --> 00:31:50.360
But the reason we want to write
this form-- because this form

00:31:50.360 --> 00:31:52.109
have a very nice
geometric interpretation.

00:31:54.580 --> 00:32:00.290
This has a very nice
geometric interpretation

00:32:00.290 --> 00:32:17.766
because delta SE, delta
phi c evaluated at z, x

00:32:17.766 --> 00:32:23.320
should be equal to phi c z, x.

00:32:23.320 --> 00:32:35.490
And this pi, which is
the canonical momentum

00:32:35.490 --> 00:32:52.460
conjugate to phi treating
the z direction as time.

00:32:58.690 --> 00:33:02.090
This z direction
treating as time.

00:33:02.090 --> 00:33:06.810
And so this pi c just means
