00:35:16.440 --> 00:35:24.710
you do the valuation over the
final value of your location.

00:35:24.710 --> 00:35:29.320
This gives you the momentum
at that point at P1.

00:35:29.320 --> 00:35:36.860
And if you do the
valuation over delta X0,

